text: Yelena Ivanovna Kondulainen (; born 9 April 1958 as Lembi Kontulainen) is a Russian actress, Honored Artist of the Russian Federation (2002),Почётное звание присвоено указом президента № 116 от 31 января 2002 года and pop singer. == References == == Other websites == * Category:1958 births Category:Living people Category:Russian singers Category:21st-century Russian singers Category:Soviet actors Category:Russian movie actors
